<view><block s-if="{{isload}}"><block><form data-event-opts="{{[['submit',[['subform',['$event']]]]]}}" bindsubmit="__e"><view class="form-box"><view class="form-item"><view class="f1">名称：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="name" placeholder="请填写名称" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.name}}"/></view></view><block s-if="{{info.sound_input_appid}}"><block><view class="form-item"><view class="f1">友商编号：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="client_id" placeholder="请填写友商编号" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.client_id}}"/></view></view><view class="form-item"><view class="f1">友商密钥：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="client_secret" placeholder="请填写友商密钥" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.client_secret}}"/></view></view></block></block><view class="form-item"><view class="f1">设备号：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="device_sn" placeholder="请填写设备号" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.device_sn}}"/></view></view><view class="form-item"><view class="f1">消息密钥：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="device_sign" placeholder="请填写友商密钥" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.device_sign}}"/></view></view><view class="form-item flex-col"><view class="f1">选择门店：</view><view class="f2" style="line-height:50rpx;width:100%;"><checkbox-group class="radio-group" name="mdid" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['bindMendianChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><block s-for="$root.l0 trackBy item.$orig.id" s-for-item="item" s-for-index="__i0__"><label><checkbox value="{{''+item.$orig.id}}" checked="{{item.m0?true:false}}"></checkbox>{{''+item.$orig.name+''}}</label></block></checkbox-group></view></view><view class="form-item flex-col"><view class="f1">播报订单：</view><view class="f2" style="line-height:50rpx;width:100%;"><checkbox-group class="radio-group" name="play_content" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['bindMendianChange',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><label><checkbox value="all" checked="{{$root.m1?true:false}}"></checkbox>全部</label><label><checkbox value="maidan" checked="{{$root.m2?true:false}}"></checkbox>买单</label><label><checkbox value="shop" checked="{{$root.m3?true:false}}"></checkbox>商城</label><label><checkbox value="collage" checked="{{$root.m4?true:false}}"></checkbox>多人拼团</label></checkbox-group></view></view><view class="form-item" style="display:block;"><view style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><view class="f1">买单付款播报：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="custom_content" placeholder="请填写买单付款播报" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.custom_content}}"/></view></view><view style="color:#999;line-height:38rpx;margin-bottom:20rpx;font-size:24rpx;">[金额]、[实付金额]为动态数据，会自动替换；如播报多个动态数据中间使用“+”连接，如：收款[金额]+到账[实付金额]</view></view><view class="form-item" style="display:block;"><view style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><view class="f1">商城订单播报：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="custom_content_shop" placeholder="请填写商城订单播报" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.custom_content_shop}}"/></view></view><view style="color:#999;line-height:38rpx;margin-bottom:20rpx;font-size:24rpx;">[金额]、[实付金额]为动态数据，会自动替换；如播报多个动态数据中间使用“+”连接，如：收款[金额]+到账[实付金额]</view></view><view class="form-item" style="display:block;"><view style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><view class="f1">拼团订单播报：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="custom_content_collage" placeholder="请填写拼团订单播报" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.custom_content_collage}}"/></view></view><view style="color:#999;line-height:38rpx;margin-bottom:20rpx;font-size:24rpx;">[金额]、[实付金额]为动态数据，会自动替换；如播报多个动态数据中间使用“+”连接，如：收款[金额]+到账[实付金额]</view></view><view class="form-item" style="display:block;"><view style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><view class="f1">进入买单页播报：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="intomaidan_content" placeholder="请填写进入买单页面播报" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.intomaidan_content}}"/></view></view><view style="color:#999;line-height:38rpx;margin-bottom:20rpx;font-size:24rpx;">自定义文字，如填写文字：点；不填写信息不播报</view></view><view class="form-item" style="display:block;"><view style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;"><view class="f1">付款页取消支付播报：</view><view class="f2"><input type="text" name="cancelpay_content" placeholder="请填写付款页面取消支付播报" placeholder-style="color:#888" value="{{info.cancelpay_content}}"/></view></view><view style="color:#999;line-height:38rpx;margin-bottom:20rpx;font-size:24rpx;">自定义文字，如填写文字：顾客取消支付；不填写信息不播报</view></view><view class="form-item"><view>状态：</view><view><radio-group class="radio-group" name="status" data-event-opts="{{[['change',[['',['$event']]]]]}}" bindchange="__e"><label><radio value="1" checked="{{info.status==1?true:false}}"></radio>显示</label><label><radio value="0" checked="{{!info||info.status==0?true:false}}"></radio>隐藏</label></radio-group></view></view></view><button class="savebtn" style="{{('background:linear-gradient(90deg,'+$root.m5+' 0%,rgba('+$root.m6+',0.8) 100%)')}}" form-type="submit">提交</button><block s-if="{{info.id}}"><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['todel',['$event']]]]]}}" class="button text-btn" bindtap="__e">删除</button></block><view style="height:50rpx;"></view></form></block></block><block s-if="{{loading}}"><loading vue-id="12f4542e-1"></loading></block></view>